title: 'What should I be for Halloween?' Find out with this personality quiz
text:
We know what's popular -- witches, zombies, "Star Wars" and super heroes -- but which Halloween costume is the truest expression of your personality?
Stumped for inspiration? Just answer the questions below and "voila!" instant dress-up idea for that 'gram-worthy Halloween party you just RSVP'd to.
